genresAdvancedInfo.name: pops orchestra
genresAdvancedInfo.description: A grandiose and sophisticated genre that features a full orchestra with a focus on popular music. The sound is rich and dynamic, with arrangements that showcase the power of strings, brass, and percussion. Pops orchestra music is often used in film scores and live performances, and it can evoke a range of emotions from excitement to nostalgia.
